Package: SimRVPedigree
Type: Package
Title: Simulate Pedigrees Ascertained for a Rare Disease
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Christina Nieuwoudt, Jinko Graham
Maintainer: Christina Nieuwoudt <cnieuwou@sfu.ca>
Description: Routines to simulate pedigrees ascertained for a rare disease.
    Provides functions to: (1) simulate a sample of pedigrees which have been
    ascertained on the basis of containing multiple family members affected by
    a rare disease according to a particular study design, and (2) manipulate
    simulated pedigrees for the purpose of analyses.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.5)
Imports:
    kinship2 (>= 1.6.4),
    dplyr (>= 0.4.3),
    stats (>= 3.3.0)
Suggests:
    doParallel (>= 1.0.10),
    doRNG (>= 1.6),
    graphics (>= 3.3.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
License: GNU General Public License
LazyData: TRUE
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
VignetteBuilder: knitr
